OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775063147
OL,3,CFamily's desperate plea for drug that
OL,4,Ccould slow teen's degenerative disease
OL,6,FITV News Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FMel Barham spoke to Jake and his
OL,8,Ffamily.
OL,10,FA teenage boy has travelled 1,000
OL,11,Fmiles to receive vital treatment for a
OL,12,Frare neurological condition.
OL,14,FJake McGregor-How, 16, has
OL,15,FFriedreich's Ataxia, a degenerative
OL,16,Fbrain condition that affects balance,
OL,17,Fmobility, speech and eventually the
OL,18,Fheart.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775063147
OL,3,CFamily's desperate plea for drug that
OL,4,Ccould slow teen's degenerative disease
OL,6,FA drug that slows the progression of
OL,7,Fthe disease, Omaveloxolone, has been
OL,8,Fproven to be safe and is available in
OL,9,Fparts of Europe and USA, however it is
OL,10,Fnot currently available in the UK.
OL,12,FThanks to the generosity of strangers,
OL,13,Fhis family, who set out to raise
OL,14,F#300,000 in January, received #100,000
OL,15,Fin donations, meaning they take the
OL,16,Fteenager to Germany to receive three
OL,17,Fmonths of the life-saving medication.
OL,19,FHe has only been on the drug for a
OL,20,Fcouple of weeks but already says he is
OL,21,Fnoticing some cognitive improvement.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775063147
OL,3,CFamily's desperate plea for drug that
OL,4,Ccould slow teen's degenerative disease
OL,6,FBut his family still need the extra
OL,7,Fmoney to ensure Jake can get a year's
OL,8,Fsupply of the drug - which they will
OL,9,Fneed to fundraise for all over again
OL,10,Fnext year.
OL,12,FJake's family has now started a
OL,13,Fpetition calling on the government to
OL,14,Flicence the drug in the UK - which the
OL,15,FNational Institute for Health and Care
OL,16,FExcellence (NICE) says it did not
OL,17,Fapprove the drug as its manufacturer,
OL,18,FBiogen, "withdrew its evidence
OL,19,Fsubmission".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775063147
OL,3,CFamily's desperate plea for drug that
OL,4,Ccould slow teen's degenerative disease
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News in January, Jake
OL,7,Ffrom Mossley Hill, Liverpool, said:
OL,8,F"It's quite hard to walk around and
OL,9,Fnavigate my surroundings. I'm really
OL,10,Fclumsy. All my friends know me as the
OL,11,Fclumsy one before I was even diagnosed.
OL,13,F"I have brain fog, I can't really
OL,14,Ffocus that well. It's quite difficult
OL,15,Fto be honest."
OL,17,FAfter the appeal went on ITV Granada
OL,18,FReports, raising tens of thousands of
OL,19,Fpounds, Jake said: "It was
OL,20,Fheartwarming to see how many people
OL,21,Funderstood.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775063147
OL,3,CFamily's desperate plea for drug that
OL,4,Ccould slow teen's degenerative disease
OL,6,F"I didn't expect so much support, it's
OL,7,Fso nice.
OL,9,F"I just want to say thank you - an
OL,10,Funconditional thank you."
OL,12,F"You've made a difference - the
OL,13,Fcompassion, generosity," Ann McGregor,
OL,14,FJake's grandmother added.
OL,16,FJake said: "It's really hard to fathom
OL,17,Fhow much of a task it is to raise this
OL,18,Fmuch money and the fact we're getting
OL,19,Fsomewhere is really great."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775063147
OL,3,CFamily's desperate plea for drug that
OL,4,Ccould slow teen's degenerative disease
OL,6,FMel Barham spoke to Jake and his
OL,7,Ffamily in January when they launched
OL,8,Ftheir fundraising effort
OL,10,FJake was diagnosed shortly after he
OL,11,Flost his mum to a rare cancer in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775063147
OL,3,CFamily's desperate plea for drug that
OL,4,Ccould slow teen's degenerative disease
OL,6,F"It is an expensive drug we know
OL,7,Fthat," Ann said. "But you do have to
OL,8,Ffactor in, even i you don't look on
OL,9,Fcompassionate grounds, if you look on
OL,10,Flogical grounds, people who don't get
OL,11,Fthe drug will unfortunately
OL,12,Fdeteriorate and they will need a lot
OL,13,Fof care from the NHS which will cost a
OL,14,Flot of money, so you have to weigh
OL,15,Fthat up as well."
OL,17,FThe drug is widely available in parts
OL,18,Fof Europe and North America, but not
OL,19,Fin the UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775063147
OL,3,CFamily's desperate plea for drug that
OL,4,Ccould slow teen's degenerative disease
OL,6,FPaul How, Jake's dad, added: "It seems
OL,7,Fquite unjust, the German neurologist
OL,8,Fwas quite startled that we couldn't
OL,9,Factually access the drug."
OL,11,FHe has now released a charity single
OL,12,Fin a bid to continue the fundraising.
OL,14,F"It's actually a song I wrote for
OL,15,FJake's mum before she got ill, it was
OL,16,Fplayed at Gaynor's funeral, and it
OL,17,Fjust seemed quite a fitting thing to
OL,18,Fbe able to help Jake really," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775063147
OL,3,CFamily's desperate plea for drug that
OL,4,Ccould slow teen's degenerative disease
OL,6,FIn January, a NICE spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"NICE was unable to make a
OL,8,Frecommendation on Omaveloxolone
OL,9,F(Skyclarys) for treating Friedreich's
OL,10,Fataxia in people 16 years and over
OL,11,Fbecause Biogen withdrew its evidence
OL,12,Fsubmission.
OL,14,F"We provide rigorous, independent
OL,15,Fassessment of complex evidence for new
OL,16,Fhealth technologies to make sure the
OL,17,FNHS can continue to offer the most
OL,18,Feffective treatment options to
OL,19,Feveryone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775063147
OL,3,CFamily's desperate plea for drug that
OL,4,Ccould slow teen's degenerative disease
OL,6,F"NICE must balance the benefits that a
OL,7,Fnew medicine offers with the savings
OL,8,Fthat have to be made from other vital
OL,9,Fpatient services elsewhere in the
OL,10,Fsystem to pay for it.
OL,12,F"Unfortunately, NICE cannot recommend
OL,13,Fa drug if the company does not take
OL,14,Fpart in our work, and the outcome of
OL,15,Fan evaluation cannot be assumed. In
OL,16,Fmore than 9 out of 10 cases in the
OL,17,Fpast year we have approved drugs for
OL,18,Froutine use in the NHS."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
